*1. "Uvek se smejem budalama* koje misle da su u pravu." (I always laugh at fools who think they are right.)

2. "Da li će te budalošću* da se istakneš?" (Will you stand out with your foolishness?)

3. "Ne mogu da verujem da si to uradio, budalo!"* (I can't believe you did that, fool!)

4. "Ne dolazi u obzir da činim nešto tako budalaštine*." (It's not an option to do something so stupid.)

5. "Ne treba da se stidiš zbog budalastih* postupaka." (You should not be ashamed of foolish actions.)